The "Live Activity Logs" page shows details about a build-in-progress, including the last 10/25/50/100 lines of the log file. However, there is no link to the full log file, so that you could see any messages at the top of the log. Such a log file exists at a url like

{{https://HOST/download/BUILD-NAME/build_logs/BUILD-NAME-2667.log}}

You could show a *link to full build* on the same line as the 10/25/50/100 dropdown.
